"title": "3110: Holy Spirit, titles and names of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "3110",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The names and terms for the Holy Spirit relate to his power, activity and presence in the world, often indicating the nature of his actions or the gifts which he conveys to believers.</p>\n<h2>Titles relating the Holy Spirit to God</h2>\n<h3>The Spirit of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:2\">GEN 1:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:38\">GEN 41:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:10\">1SA 10:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam19:20\">1SA 19:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam19:23\">1SA 19:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:9\">ROM 8:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:11\">1CO 6:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:3\">2CO 3:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:30\">EPH 4:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:3\">PHP 3:3</a></p>\n<h3>The Spirit of the LORD</h3>\n<p>The Spirit empowered the judges to deliver the people:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:10\">JDG 3:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:34\">JDG 6:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg11:29\">JDG 11:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg13:25\">JDG 13:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:6\">JDG 14:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:19\">JDG 14:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg15:14\">JDG 15:14</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:6\">1SA 10:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:13\">1SA 16:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam23:2\">2SA 23:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:2\">ISA 11:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1\">ISA 61:1</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:17\">2CO 3:17</a></p>\n<h2>Forms of reference to the Spirit of God</h2>\n<h3>My Spirit</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:3\">GEN 6:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:1\">ISA 30:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:21\">ISA 59:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:28-Joel2:29\">JOL 2:28–2:29</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag2:5\">HAG 2:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech4:6\">ZEC 4:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech6:8\">ZEC 6:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:18\">MAT 12:18</a></p>\n<h3>His Spirit</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa34:16\">ISA 34:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:10-Isa63:11\">ISA 63:10–63:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech7:12\">ZEC 7:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:11\">ROM 8:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:22\">EPH 2:22</a></p>\n<h3>Your Spirit</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:20\">NEH 9:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:30\">NEH 9:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:11\">PSA 51:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:7\">PSA 139:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps143:10\">PSA 143:10</a></p>\n<h3>The Spirit of your Father</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:20\">MAT 10:20</a></p>\n<h3>The promised Holy Spirit</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:33\">ACT 2:33</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:13\">EPH 1:13</a></p>\n<h3>The Spirit of him who raised Jesus from the dead</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:11\">ROM 8:11</a></p>\n<h3>The spirit of the gods</h3>\n<p>Seen from a pagan viewpoint:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:8-Dan4:9\">DAN 4:8–4:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:18\">DAN 4:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:11\">DAN 5:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:14\">DAN 5:14</a></p>\n<h2>Titles relating the Holy Spirit to God the Son</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:6\">GAL 4:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:7\">ACT 16:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:9\">ROM 8:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:19\">PHP 1:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:11\">1PE 1:11</a></p>\n<h2>Titles revealing the Holy Spirit's essential nature</h2>\n<h3>The Spirit of truth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:13\">JHN 16:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:17\">JHN 14:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:26\">JHN 15:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:6\">1JN 4:6</a></p>\n<h3>The Spirit of holiness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:4\">ROM 1:4</a></p>\n<h3>The Spirit of life</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:2\">ROM 8:2</a></p>\n<h3>The Spirit of glory</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:14\">1PE 4:14</a></p>\n<h3>The eternal Spirit</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:14\">HEB 9:14</a></p>\n<h2>Titles showing the nature of the Holy Spirit's activity</h2>\n<h3>The Counsellor</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:26\">JHN 14:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:26\">JHN 15:26</a></p>\n<h3>The Spirit of wisdom and understanding</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:2\">ISA 11:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut34:9\">DEU 34:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:17\">EPH 1:17</a></p>\n<h3>The Spirit of grace and supplication</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech12:10\">ZEC 12:10</a></p>\n<h3>The Spirit of sonship</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:15\">ROM 8:15</a></p>\n<h3>The Spirit of judgment and fire</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa4:4\">ISA 4:4</a></p>",
